rpc error: code = Internal desc = failed to prepare order: failed to get product #\\\"\"2ZYFJ3GM2N\\\"\"\"\",\"\"http.req.id\"\":\"\"74390cbb-6be9-4c45-bf21-7a27406d0bf3\"\",\"\"http.req.method\"\":\"\"POST\"\",\"\"http.req.path\"\":\"\"/cart/checkout\"\",\"\"message\"\":\"\"request error\"\",\"\"session\"\":\"\"1e5f9e35-da29-4faa-b2cf-9b5a860247a9\"\",\"\"severity\"\":\"\"error\"\",\"\"timestamp\"\":\"\"2025-06-21T01:11:49.126644553Z\"\"}\",出现次数:1\n", "unique_entities": {"pod_name": ["frontend-1", "frontend-2", "productcatalogservice-0", "frontend-0", "productcatalogservice-1"], "service_name": ["frontend", "productcatalogservice"], "node_name": ["aiops-k8s-06", "aiops-k8s-08", "aiops-k8s-04"]}, "matched_anomaly": "Please analyze the abnormal event between 2025-06-21T01:10:10Z and 2025-06-21T01:28:10Z and provide the root cause.", "time_range": "2025-06-21 01:10:10+00:00 to 2025-06-21 01:28:10+00:00"}, "log_data_collected": true, "trace_analysis_findings": "基于收集到的监控数据，我已经完成了对异常事件的初始扫描分析。以下是详细的发现：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"error_ratio\",\n    \"frontend->productcatalogservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->productcatalogservice\",\n    \"recommendationservice->productcatalogservice\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"ProductCatalogService响应时间从正常约10ms激增至39,000ms（延迟倍数约4,000倍），涉及所有调用方\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\", \n      \"evidence\": \"出现大量'Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable'错误，表明TiDB数据库区域不可用\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Frontend服务出现HTTP 500错误，是由于ProductCatalogService不可用导致的连锁反应\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Checkout服务下单失败，具体错误为'failed to get product'，同样源于ProductCatalogService不可用\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**关键发现总结：**\n\n1. **核心问题**: ProductCatalogService出现严重性能异常，响应时间从约10ms增加到39,000ms（约4,000倍延迟增长）\n\n2. **错误根源**: 数据库错误\"Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable\"表明TiDB数据库的区域不可用问题\n\n3. **影响范围**: 该异常影响了所有依赖ProductCatalogService的服务：\n   - Frontend服务（HTTP 500错误）\n   - Checkout服务（下单失败）\n   - Recommendation服务（性能轻微波动）\n\n4. **根因定位**: ProductCatalogService是最下游的异常服务，且直接与数据库交互，因此是本次异常的根本原因。", "log_analysis_findings": "基于收集到的监控数据，我已经完成了对异常时间段的初始扫描分析。以下是分析结果：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable\", \"rpc error\", \"code = Unknown\", \"code = Internal\", \"failed to query product by id\", \"failed to get product recommendations\", \"failed to complete the order\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"数据库区域不可用导致产品查询失败，出现 Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable 错误\",\n      \"evidence\": \"productcatalogservice-0 和 productcatalogservice-1 出现大量 'failed to query product by id: Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable' 警告日志，出现次数分别为76次和161次\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"由于 productcatalogservice 数据库问题导致前端服务无法正常获取产品信息，出现 rpc error 和产品检索失败\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend 服务出现大量 'could not retrieve product: rpc error: code = Unknown desc = Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable' 错误日志\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"order processing system\",\n      \"reason\": \"订单处理流程因无法获取产品信息而失败，出现 failed to complete the order 错误\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend-2 出现 'failed to complete the order: rpc error: code = Internal desc = failed to prepare order: failed to get product' 错误日志\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 分析要点总结：\n\n1. **主要错误模式**：所有错误都围绕数据库\"Region is unavailable\"问题展开\n2. **影响范围**：涉及 frontend 和 productcatalogservice 两个服务\n3. **错误传播路径**：\n   - productcatalogservice 无法访问数据库区域\n   - frontend 调用 productcatalogservice 时出现 RPC 错误\n   - 最终影响用户购物车、产品推荐和订单完成功能\n\n4. **关键发现**：\n   - productcatalogservice 是问题的源头组件\n   - 错误主要集中在数据库连接层面（Error 9005）\n   - 故障影响从 01:10:52 开始，持续到至少 01:24:08", "metric_analysis_findings": "{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\n    \"memory_usage\",\n    \"error_ratio\",\n    \"client_error_ratio\",\n    \"failed_query_ops\",\n    \"pod_cpu_usage\",\n    \"duration_99th\",\n    \"rrt\",\n    \"server_error_ratio\",\n    \"store_unhealth_count\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"tidb-tidb\",\n      \"reason\": \"Significant increase in memory_usage (change_ratio: 0.6141) and failed_query_ops (change_ratio: 2.0).\",\n      \"evidence\": \"memory_usage: normal_median=1277841408.0, fault_median=677435392.0; failed_query_ops: normal_median=0.0, fault_median=44.0.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"High error_ratio (change_ratio: 2.0) and client_error_ratio (change_ratio: 2.0).\",\n      \"evidence\": \"error_ratio: normal_median=0.0, fault_median=50.0; client_error_ratio: normal_median=0.0, fault_median=50.0.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"High error_ratio (change_ratio: 2.0) and client_error_ratio (change_ratio: 2.0).\",\n      \"evidence\": \"error_ratio: normal_median=0.0, fault_median=59.07; client_error_ratio: normal_median=0.0, fault_median=59.07.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"High error_ratio (change_ratio: 2.0) and client_error_ratio (change_ratio: 2.0).\",\n      \"evidence\": \"error_ratio: normal_median=0.0, fault_median=47.69; client_error_ratio: normal_median=0.0, fault_median=47.69.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"High server_error_ratio (change_ratio: 2.0) and error_ratio (change_ratio: 2.0).\",\n      \"evidence\": \"server_error_ratio: normal_median=0.0, fault_median=26.97; error_ratio: normal_median=0.0, fault_median=26.97.\"\n    },\n    {\